condition.narrative: ANEP shall review with the Bank and the Borrowe, by April 15 and October 15 of each year, starting on April 15, 2003, the reportreferreded in section 207 (b).
Ensure that an MIS satisfactory to the Bank be functioning and fully implemented in at least 90% of all schools with more than 50students.
Furnish to the Bank as soon as available, but in any case not later than 6 months after the end of each year, the audit reportissued by independent auditors acceptable to the Bank,
Prepare and furnish to the Bank, on or about March 15 and September 15, a semi-annual report integrating the results of themonitoring and evaluation activities performed on the progress achieved...
